    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/JuliaWeb/URIs.jl\">URIs.jl</a> is a package by itself, and <a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=HTTP.jl&amp;type=Repositories\">HTTP.jl</a> re-exports that functionality from it. So you can directly <code>add URIs</code> if you don't need other functionality from <a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=HTTP.jl&amp;type=Repositories\">HTTP.jl</a>.</p>",
